Actor: DevOps Engineer | SLA: 4 hours | Uses: TP-007</bpmn:documentation>
      </bpmn:userTask>
      <bpmn:userTask id="Task_T3213" name="T-3.2.1.3: Integrate 7-Stage DevSecOps Pipeline">
        <bpmn:documentation>Integrate 7-stage DevSecOps security pipeline (pre-commit through production monitoring).
Actor: Security Engineer / DevOps | SLA: 1 day</bpmn:documentation>
      </bpmn:userTask>
      <bpmn:userTask id="Task_T3221" name="T-3.2.2.1: Configure APM &amp; Tracing">
        <bpmn:documentation>Configure application performance monitoring, distributed tracing, and log aggregation.
Actor: SRE / DevOps | SLA: 4 hours | Uses: TP-009</bpmn:documentation>
      </bpmn:userTask>
      <bpmn:userTask id="Task_T3222" name="T-3.2.2.2: Create Dashboards &amp; SLO/SLI">
        <bpmn:documentation>Create dashboards, alerts, and SLO/SLI monitoring configurations.
Actor: SRE | SLA: 4 hours</bpmn:documentation>
      </bpmn:userTask>
      <bpmn:userTask id="Task_T3231" name="T-3.2.3.1: Configure AI Agents">
        <bpmn:documentation>Configure applicable AI agents for the initiative (Code Generation, Code Review, Testing, Documentation).
Actor: AI Platform Team | SLA: 4 hours | Uses: TP-004</bpmn:documentation>
      </bpmn:userTask>
      <bpmn:businessRuleTask id="Task_T3232" name="T-3.2.3.2: Execute DMN-DT-008 (Agent Thresholds)">
        <bpmn:documentation>Set agent confidence thresholds and human-in-the-loop escalation rules per risk tier using DMN-DT-008.
Hit Policy: Unique (U) | Actor: DMN Engine / AI Platform | SLA: 1 hour</bpmn:documentation>
      </bpmn:businessRuleTask>
      <bpmn:endEvent id="End_SP32" />

      <bpmn:sequenceFlow id="f_sp32_1" sourceRef="Start_SP32" targetRef="Task_T3211" />
      <bpmn:sequenceFlow id="f_sp32_2" sourceRef="Task_T3211" targetRef="Task_T3212" />
      <bpmn:sequenceFlow id="f_sp32_3" sourceRef="Task_T3212" targetRef="Task_T3213" />
