Actor: Data Engineer | SLA: 1 day</bpmn:documentation>
      </bpmn:userTask>
      <bpmn:userTask id="Task_T3412" name="T-3.4.1.2: Configure Data Governance Controls">
        <bpmn:documentation>Configure data governance controls: masking, encryption, access logging, retention policies.
Actor: Data Engineer / DPO | SLA: 1 day</bpmn:documentation>
      </bpmn:userTask>
      <bpmn:userTask id="Task_T3421" name="T-3.4.2.1: Register APIs in Gateway">
        <bpmn:documentation>Register APIs in enterprise API gateway with rate limiting, authentication, and versioning.
Actor: Integration Engineer | SLA: 4 hours | Uses: TP-008</bpmn:documentation>
      </bpmn:userTask>
      <bpmn:userTask id="Task_T3422" name="T-3.4.2.2: Configure Event Bus &amp; MQ">
